362
00:29:54,325 --> 00:29:55,450
Posso tentar de novo?

363
00:29:58,575 --> 00:29:59,867
Nunca desistimos.

364
00:30:44,908 --> 00:30:46,075
Isso aí!

365
00:30:50,450 --> 00:30:55,825
O primeiro homem a usar
